VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT require\s*\(\s*['"]electron['"]\s*\)\s*\.\s*remote|@electron/remote
WHEN EXPR MISSING:contextBridge|ipcRenderer|ipcMain && MISSING:test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects use of Electron's deprecated remote module in renderer processes.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Remote Module Usage (Deprecated).
